OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will begin dry with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. A few showers
OL,7,Fwill begin in the west from mid
OL,8,Fmorning before spreading east through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FScattered evening showers
OL,12,Fwill clear from the late evening
OL,13,Fleaving dry conditions and clear
OL,14,Fspells for a time. Scattered showers
OL,15,Fwill return towards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,18,Fscattered morning showers. Showers
OL,19,Fclear from the early afternoon before
OL,20,Fcloud and rain spread east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
